ion"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"品名调价总金额内部转移相应调整销售价格影响当年财政收入其中　备注农民受益城市人民受益总计78723366296674-35420+35276+1441．(+)号表示提价或增加；(-)号表示降价或减少。(以下各表均同)　2．影响当年财政收入金额，实际执行结果是会有出入的。因为：(1)方案系按年初调价计算的，实际调价是在全年陆续执行的；(2)去年决定的调价方案，有一部分(如电子基础产品等)是在今年执行；(3)进口手表的销售价格已经提高，这是增加财政收的，未列入计划表内　　　　　　　#提价+32188　　-24078+28605-4527降价-46535-11342+66714671　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　农副产品收购价格+2918814366674-21078+25605-4527　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　工业品销售价格-5305963　-4342+2671+1671农业生产资料出厂　　　　　　价格-45954595　　　　重工业品出厂价格-2963529635　　　　调整地区差价、城　　　　　　乡差价　　　-10000　　#农产品+3000　　-3000+3000　工业品-7000　　-7000+4000+3000","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"1973年产品收购价格调整计划","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"表5—3—12","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","type":"appellation"},{"text":"","